modName: Custom palette (Lut) for Snapdragon Prime ENB v4.33
summary: Only Red palette and more for Snapdragon Prime ENB. naturally, You need Snapdragon Prime ENB
descriptionHtml:
[center]
This file will add custom palette (4~12) to Snapdragon Prime ENB by tetrodoxin.

Custom palette 4~6 [color=#ff0000][size=3]Only Red [/size][/color]palette.

Custom Palette 7~12 is not useful, this files only for me.




1. You need

Snapdragon Prime ENB by tetrodoxin
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/[/url]?

and

Optional, You can use Goma LUTs
[url=http://tetrodoxin.tumblr.com/post/174280561207/snapdragon-prime-enb-goma-luts-hello-just-a]http://tetrodoxin.tumblr.com/post/174280561207/snapdragon-prime-enb-goma-luts-hello-just-a
[/url]﻿





2. Download my file, and Extract.






3. Copy and paste enbseries folder

Overwrite enbeffect.fx and enbeffect.fx.ini file





Example
